 531:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c **** /**
 532:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @brief  Generates a 32-bit random number.
 533:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @note   This function checks value of RNG_FLAG_DRDY flag to know if valid
 534:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         random number is available in the DR register (RNG_FLAG_DRDY flag set
 535:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         whenever a random number is available through the RNG_DR register).
 536:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         After transitioning from 0 to 1 (random number available),
 537:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         RNG_FLAG_DRDY flag remains high until output buffer becomes empty after reading
 538:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         four words from the RNG_DR register, i.e. further function calls
ARM GAS  C:\Users\bku598\AppData\Local\Temp\ccauXdwZ.s 			page 15


 539:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         will immediately return a new u32 random number (additional words are
 540:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         available and can be read by the application, till RNG_FLAG_DRDY flag remains high).
 541:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @note   When no more random number data is available in DR register, RNG_FLAG_DRDY
 542:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *         flag is automatically cleared.
 543:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @param  hrng pointer to a RNG_HandleTypeDef structure that contains
 544:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   *                the configuration information for RNG.
 545:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @param  random32bit pointer to generated random number variable if successful.
 546:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rng.c ****   * @retval HAL status
